<!--#!autodoc
Sitetree Page: add form

This form is used as the base "add page" form for Sitetree pages. See also [[form-sitetreepageeditform]].

>>> When an add page form is rendered, it gets mixed in with any forms that are defined for the *page type* that is being added.
-->
<form>
	<tab id="main" sortorder="10">
		<fieldset id="main" sortorder="10">
			<field sortorder="20" binding="page.slug" control="vnautoSlug" required="true" autoSlug="true" basedOn="title" />
		</fieldset>
	</tab>
</form>